doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="/css/Guidelines.css")
    link(rel="shortcut icon", href="/media/Qastra.jpeg", type="image/x-icon")
    title Qastra: Privacy Policy

  body
    include ./PreLoader.pug
    .background
      img(src="/media/interface-background-3.jpeg", alt="")
      .shade

    .random-pattern-1
      img(src="/media/interface-random-pattern-4.png", alt="")

    .random-pattern-2
      img(src="/media/interface-random-pattern-3.png", alt="")

    .random-pattern-3
      img(src="/media/interface-human.png", alt="")

    .random-pattern-4
      img(src="/media/interface-calculator.png", alt="")

    .mains
      h1 Qastra
      h4 One Question Closer to Clarity
      h1 Privacy Policy

    .guide
      .box
        h4 🔒 Data Collection
        p We collect only the necessary information you provide during sign-up, like your name and email, to enhance your experience on Qastra.

      .box
        h4 🧠 Usage Data
        p We may log usage patterns (like questions posted or answered) to improve our services. This data is anonymized and not shared with third parties.

      .box
        h4 🛡️ Data Security
        p Your data is stored securely with encryption practices. We actively work to protect your information against unauthorized access.

      .box
        h4 📩 Email Communication
        p We may send occasional updates or notifications. You can opt out at any time via your settings.

      .box
        h4 📁 Data Sharing
        p We do not sell or rent your personal data. Limited sharing may occur only with trusted services (like analytics) under strict agreements.

      .box
        h4 🧽 Cookies
        p Qastra uses cookies to remember your preferences and enhance functionality. You can control cookie settings through your browser.

      .box
        h4 🔁 Third-Party Links
        p We are not responsible for the privacy practices of linked external sites. Please review their policies when leaving Qastra.

      .box
        h4 📝 User Rights
        p You have the right to request, update, or delete your personal data at any time. Just reach out to our support team.

      .box
        h4 🔧 Policy Updates
        p Our privacy policy may change over time. We'll notify you of major updates and always keep the latest version available here.

      .box
        h4 💬 Contact Us
        p For any privacy-related questions, concerns, or data requests, please contact our team through the Help section.

    script(src="/js/Guidelines.js")
